      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) in ambient dry conditions at room temperature per ASTM F1717. Physiological saline environment and elevated temperature conditions were not evaluated. Only one loading rate was assessed, limiting coverage of the intended use environment. Achieved level 2 does not meet required level 3 for this factor."
