      "rationale": "E/uval computed as (|FEA mean - experimental mean|) / combined uncertainty. Results: stiffness E/uval = 0.84 (4.1% difference); yield force E/uval = 1.12 (5.7% difference); force at 40 mm E/uval = 0.97 (3.9% difference). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria across both laboratories. Output comparison factor met at required level 3."
